snippet.title: Thank You - 1,000 Shoutouts!!!
snippet.description:
Thank you :) 

A little over a year ago I had 0 subscribers on this channel. Now, to see that we have grown to over 1,000 is truly amazing. I wanted to thank you each individually, so I did :)

Thank you for being one of my very first 1,000 subscribers and I'm excited to be on this journey with you :)
